item.description: Who am I? I am currently a sophomore in New York University, majored in computer science (planned to be an honored track). I am a traveller who’ve been to America, China, Australia, Swizerland, and Greece. Huge fan of Computer games/ Computers I always dream of becoming a game designer some day.
